msgctxt "116_Shizuka"
msgid "Nothing better than a good meal in a relaxed environment, don't you think?"
msgstr "Nada mejor que una buena comida en un ambiente relajado, ¿no cree?"

msgctxt "128_Player"
msgid "Let's go in."
msgstr "Entremos."

msgctxt "152_Shizuka"
msgid "Nothing better than a good meal in a relaxed environment, don't you think?"
msgstr "Nada mejor que una buena comida en un ambiente relajado, ¿no cree?"

msgctxt "164_Player"
msgid "Hold on a sec. I just realized that I'm short on cash."
msgstr "Espera un segundo. Me acabo de dar cuenta de que estoy corto de efectivo."

msgctxt "176_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, really?"
msgstr "¿En serio?"

msgctxt "188_Player"
msgid "Yeah. Sorry..."
msgstr "Sí. Lo siento..."

msgctxt "200_Shizuka"
msgid "No, I'm the one who should apologize. I asked you out and inconvenienced you like this."
msgstr "No, soy yo quien debería pedir disculpas. Lo invité a salir y lo incomodé de esa forma."

msgctxt "212_Player"
msgid "(I'd better remember to bring enough cash next time...)"
msgstr "(Será mejor que recuerde llevar suficiente dinero en efectivo la próxima vez...)"

msgctxt "320_Shizuka"
msgid "Ah, that was delicious."
msgstr "Ah, eso estuvo delicioso."

msgctxt "332_Player"
msgid "Glad you liked it."
msgstr "Me alegra que te haya gustado."

msgctxt "344_Shizuka"
msgid "Thank you for the meal, sir. May I ask you to take me out again sometime?"
msgstr "Gracias por la comida, señor. ¿Puedo pedirle que me invite a salir de nuevo en algún momento?"

msgctxt "356_Player"
msgid "Definitely."
msgstr "Por supuesto."

msgctxt "368_Shizuka"
msgid "Then, until we meet again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392_Shizuka"
msgid "Thank you for treating me. That was quite good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404_Player"
msgid "Glad to hear it."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "416_Shizuka"
msgid "May I ask you to take me out again sometime?"
msgstr "¿Puedo pedirle que vuelva a salir conmigo alguna vez?"

msgctxt "428_Player"
msgid "Definitely."
msgstr "Por supuesto."

msgctxt "440_Shizuka"
msgid "Then, until we meet again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464_Shizuka"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "476_Player"
msgid "Hmm? Something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "488_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh no, it's just... The meal was delicious, but there was something I didn't like in the food..."
msgstr "Oh no, es que... La comida estaba deliciosa, pero había algo que no me gustaba en la comida..."

msgctxt "500_Player"
msgid "Oh. Sorry to hear that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512_Shizuka"
msgid "Please don't mind me. I should be going now. I shall see you at the club..."
msgstr "Por favor, no se preocupe por mí. Debo irme. Lo veré en el club..."

msgctxt "524_Player"
